net.sf.JRecord.Details

Interface LineProvider

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CharLineProvider, DefaultLineProvider, XmlLineProvider

    public interface LineProvider
    A LineProvider creates lines for the calling program. By creating your own LineProvider, you can use your own Line's rather than the System Line / XmlLine class.
    Author:
    Bruce Martin
